ock in the morning with the papers you see. And then going to work at eight o\rquote clock. To - the other place you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 When would he come home then from the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Five o\rquote clock.
