\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 In - in with the paper - he - he didn\rquote t have a lot to do with the echoes like you know, but he\rquote 
d be in the shop like you know, we were glad for him to come home to go in the shop like you know. I never liked the shop you see, and - he never went - out with - evening papers, he went out with morning papers. 
And my mother did. And I did. But - not in the evening. We had boys in the evening you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 You would be just sort of supervising them would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Yes.
