\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 That\rquote s right, yes.
\par 
