\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Yes. Five o\rquote clock, he finished at five. And then he\rquote d have his meal, \lquote cos we\rquote 
