\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Oh we - my mother used to have lodger now and again force theirselves on her, She didn\rquote 
t want them but she used to have a - she had a lodger occasionally but not very often. Occasionally. They\rquote d come now -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Who would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Oh, strangers, you know, and they\rquote d come asking - I - I\rquote ve been sent, so and so\rquote s sent me 
here to see if you could - if you knew of anybody or - who could put me up, well mother didn\rquote t know of anybody and they were stranded and she said, well you - you know, you could come here like for the short time, but only a short time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Because you were right in the middle of Whitchurch and right on the main road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Did your mother ever pay anyone to help her in the house?
