\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Would Minnie help in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Oh yes, she\rquote d come and help us. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Not regularly. No. No. Say that}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126667\charrsid14953505  - my mother was feeling a bit }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 rough like and - she\rquote d say - say, I\rquote ll come up and give you a hand, but she wouldn\rquote t have no pay or anything. No pay. And my mother was good with her like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 She was more of a friend was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Oh friend, yes. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 You wouldn\rquote t have to pay anyone to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 What about the washing when you were a little girl, would that be done at home or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Oh - yes. Oh no. My mother was in her element when she was at the wash tub. She was in her element. Yes. Oh yes, I never l
iked it. Well I don\rquote t now either.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16346414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 Did your mother or father make or mend the family clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4927998 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1514656\charrsid14953505 No. My mother couldn\rquote t sew. I - I\rquote 
